title: I Don't Deserve Any Of This
itunes:title: I Don't Deserve Any Of This
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I have coached baseball for ten years and in those ten years I have never had a child quit my team nor have any parents ever complained about my coaching style. Well last year a parent from the opposing team yelled at me and called me out of my name. It was all over whether or not his son was safe or out during a game. Things got heated and we had a shouting match in the parking lot......
